full_summary:
### Seal and Pump Replenishment Opportunity

#### Introduction

The Department of National Defence is announcing a Request for Proposal (RFP) for the supply of Seals and Pumps, as outlined in the following notice.

#### Tender Details

*   **Reference Number:** PW-22-01016509
*   **Solicitation Number:** W8482-231065/A
*   **Tender Closing Date:** January 20, 2023, at 14:00
*   **Procurement Category:** Goods and Services (GD)
*   **Trade Agreements:** Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement, Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement, Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement, Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA), Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA), and Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA)

#### Items to be Supplied

*   GSIN: N4320, Seal Assembly, Spring Loaded (4320-20-005-7893)
	+ Part No. 343268, NCAGE: L3636 – Chesterton Co Ltd
	+ Quantity: 3 (SE) to be delivered to CFB Halifax
	+ Quantity: 2 (SE) to be delivered to CFB Esquimalt
*   GSIN: N4320, Seal Assembly, Spring Loaded (4320-20-006-9879)
	+ Part No. 344133, NCAGE: L3636 – Chesterton Co Ltd
	+ Quantity: 3 (EA) to be delivered to CFB Halifax
	+ Quantity: 10 (EA) to be delivered to CFB Esquimalt
*   GSIN: N4320, Pump, Rotary (4320-99-968-0520)
	+ Part No. T6C-003-1-L-01-E1, NCAGE: U3058 – Denyson Hydraulics UK Ltd, or
	+ Part No. T6C-003-1-L-01-B1, NCAGE: U3058 – Denyson Hydraulics UK Ltd
	+ Quantity: 3 (EA) to be delivered to CFB Esquimalt

#### Documents and Contact Information

*   Attachment: [rfp_w8482-231065_en.pdf](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/documents/pub/att/2022/12/08/5cc73cf1cd3e6
